// ______CiMqttClientInstance.ts_________________khartinger_____
// 2022-10-18 Add CiRepeaterController
// 2023-03-15 Add CiSmsStatus1Controller'
import { CiMqttClient } from './CiMqttClient'
import { ciBlind1Controller } from '@/controller/CiBlind1Controller'
import { ciButton1Controller } from '@/controller/CiButton1Controller'
import { ciButton2Controller } from '@/controller/CiButton2Controller'
import { ciDoor1Controller } from '@/controller/CiDoor1Controller'
import { ciLamp1Controller } from '@/controller/CiLamp1Controller'
import { ciMotion1Controller } from '@/controller/CiMotion1Controller'
import { ciPump1Controller } from '@/controller/CiPump1Controller'
import { ciRepeater1Controller } from '@/controller/CiRepeater1Controller'
import { ciSocket1Controller } from '@/controller/CiSocket1Controller'
import { ciSocket2Controller } from '@/controller/CiSocket2Controller'
import { ciTextarea1Controller } from '@/controller/CiTextarea1Controller'
import { ciTimeDateController } from '@/controller/CiTimeDateController'
import { ciWeather1Controller } from '@/controller/CiWeather1Controller'
import { ciWindow1Controller } from '@/controller/CiWindow1Controller'
import { ciMqttLastXController } from '@/controller/CiMqttLastXController'
import { ciZ2Mstatus1Controller } from '@/controller/CiZ2Mstatus1Controller'
import { ciSmsStatus1Controller } from '@/controller/CiSmsStatus1Controller'

export const ciMqttClientInstance = new CiMqttClient(true)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciBlind1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciButton1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciButton2Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciDoor1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciLamp1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciMotion1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciPump1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciRepeater1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciSocket1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciSocket2Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciTextarea1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciTimeDateController)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciWeather1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciWindow1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciMqttLastXController)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciZ2Mstatus1Controller)
ciMqttClientInstance.registerController(ciSmsStatus1Controller)
